highlights.title: 🔥Yang Hansen's 2024/25 CBA Highlights - Chinese center goes to Trail Blazers｜NBA Draft
highlights.description:
🇨🇳Chinese center Yang Hansen, who turns 20 this Thursday, enters the #NBA after two standout seasons with the Qingdao Eagles in the #CBA.

🔥During the 2024-25 regular season, he averaged 16.6 points, 10.5 rebounds, 3.0 assists, and 2.6 blocks per game.

summer_league.title: Yang Hansen SHOWED HIS BAG vs Warriors In Summer League | July 11, 2025
summer_league.description:
The Trail Blazers defeated the Warriors, 106-73 tonight in Golden State. Rayan Rupert contributed a team-high 23 points to go with 9 rebounds 4 assists and 2 steals, with Caleb Love of the Trail Blazers adding an additional 18 points (7-16 FG, 4-7 3P) and 6 rebounds in the game. Jackson Rowe finished with a team-high 12 points along with 3 rebounds for the Warriors in the losing effort. The Trail Blazers improve their record to 1-0 with the win, while the Warriors fall to 0-1.

news.description:
Did Portland Just Outsmart The Entire NBA with Yang Hansen?

During the 2025 NBA draft, there was a moment in the first round where simultaneous gasps of shock and confusion were let out amongst NBA fans across the world. With the 16th overall selection – just two spots outside the lottery – Portland chose Yang Hansen, a 7-foot-1 center from China. 

In today's video we look at Did Portland Just Outsmart The Entire NBA with Yang Hansen?
